{"tid":786021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【林偉駿病逝】生意受佔領運動影響 毋懼表態不怪學生：唔好搵佔中過橋","createTime":"2018-08-19T15:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T01:27:15.000Z","uid":60665,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"995a90a7b11247dd17e9c85306c2c4d2dd0ab2ef","tid":786021,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:57:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180819/58583574\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58583574&d=Na5T5XaPBVFKHouct36x3MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=4a98d289\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58583574&h=c320b3f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180819/58583574</a><br />\n<br />\n香港商人忌諱政治，甘願染紅不計其數。林偉駿是少數敢公開表達政治立場的商人，數年前佔領運動期間，不少銅鑼灣及旺角零售商嘆生意受影響，阿信屋亦然，但林偉駿並無責怪佔領的學生，指做生意難免遇上天災人禍，「佔領運動咪同打風一樣，做生意嘅人要抽個身出嚟睇件事！」<br />\n<br />\n他以碼頭工人罷工也影響其日本貨源為例，指當時生意也可維持，強調要懂變通，「你話塞住條路，但我送貨完全冇問題喎，就算送去灣仔都冇事，送去旺區咪兩日先送一次囉，唔使日日送貨嘅。你明知條路塞咪行第二條，冇理由夾硬衝入去話要落貨，我覺得唔好搵（佔中）嚟過橋，佔領咁多日，因為交通而遲開舖嘅唔多過五單，我有210幾間舖喎！」<br />\n林偉駿指生意人對佔中應該尊重雙方意見，不應為事件火上加油，「你咪當打一場三日嘅颱風，冇理由捱唔到。」他當年透露，佔中影響店舖人流，便減少折頭，除了提高毛利，亦減低運輸次數。他不諱言，佔中對香港未來肯定是好事，因學生有理念、有思想，未來十多年可為香港帶來一批新的政治人才。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9809518b555691a24b3f60621533330816f4edea","tid":786021,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"佢屋企擺毛澤東幅相"},{"pid":"722ff7c9db7de61587e5845d93b59ceea38842dd","tid":786021,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9809518b555691a24b3f60621533330816f4edea","tid":786021,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"佢屋企擺毛澤東幅相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:03:36.000Z","msg":"佢雖然拜毛魔，但唔會揞住良心做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e139eca680977056513f9b323f3d612457bf19","tid":786021,"uid":8410,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"9809518b555691a24b3f60621533330816f4edea","tid":786021,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T15:58:35.000Z","msg":"佢屋企擺毛澤東幅相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:05:45.000Z","msg":"佢係紅底但做過的事跡令人佩服，單挑超市霸權，對抗大財團玩專營權，為左係供應商攞到貨玩埋飲食消貨一條龍，yen 升令到佢入少左日本貨，之後的守業+租金係最困難。感覺大業未成就已經離世 so rip"},{"pid":"88c6a8e19e8d89fe18fdbbca04aeefcd0dba9da9","tid":786021,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6333029fe22c2fa7f84755ee792f3cdba122acc","tid":786021,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T23:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f9d8658c7130741e554757ca8f245af79bdbf1","tid":786021,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:20:57.000Z","msg":"又提佔中，仲未柒夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93211e5529c51e49aba15aa7675f627b5f24dbd","tid":786021,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T01:27:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z99TYho4Pek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz99TYho4Pek&d=Na5T5XaPBVFKHouct36x3MPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=32939577\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z99TYho4Pek</a><br />\n<br />\n今次講得幾好"}]}